# Use Case Structure
This template is used to create a use case structure for a zero-to-one product.

## Table of Contents
- [Use Case Structure](#use-case-structure)
  - [Table of Contents](#table-of-contents)
    - [**User Management**](#user-management)
    - [**Core User Loop**](#core-user-loop)
    - [**Account Management**](#account-management)


### **User Management**
Use cases related to user signup, login, and user-level account management.
* CRUD - Create, Read, Update, Delete
* single-player - A user is the only user of the system
* multi-player - A user is one of many users of the system

### **Core User Loop**
Use cases related to the [core user loop](https://www.reforge.com/blog/growth-loops) of the product.
* Happy Path - CRUD
    * user-initiated
        * notification-layer
    * system-initiated
        * notification layer
* Alt path - CRUD
* Error path - CRUD

### **Account Management**
Use cases related to account management.
* CRUD
    * billing
    * account settings
    * notification settings
    * user settings